msgstr ""

msgid "When transparent Tor is enabled, send LAN TCP DNS to Tor DNSPort (UDP was already redirected)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Block LAN DNS-over-TLS (port 853)"
msgstr ""

msgid "Drop forwarded TCP/853 from LAN to non-router destinations. Can break DoT to public resolvers; use only if you accept that tradeoff."
